name: should handle proof b coordinate swap correctly
fullName: src/__tests__/zk-verify.test.ts#Near Citizens House Shared Library Unit Tests ZK Verification verifyStoredProof Edge Cases should handle proof b coordinate swap correctly
description: The Groth16 verifier expects b coordinates in swapped order: b[i][1], b[i][0] instead of b[i][0], b[i][1]. This test verifies the swap is applied.
descriptionHtml: The Groth16 verifier expects b coordinates in swapped order: b[i][1], b[i][0] instead of b[i][0], b[i][1]. This test verifies the swap is applied.
